---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Mark Bloomfield | Your Personal AI Guy | Boulder, CO"
  description="Engineer, founder, and the person small business owners call when they want to figure out AI without the jargon. AI-Ready Websites and AI consulting from Boulder, CO."
>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="bg-green-deep py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-white-warm leading-tight mb-5">
        Engineer. Founder.<br />Your Personal AI Guy.
      </h1>
      <p class="text-cream/70 text-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        I don't do jargon. I don't do hype. I help small business owners figure out what AI is actually worth doing — and then I build it.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- MARK -->
  <section class="bg-cream py-20">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-14 items-center">
        <div>
          <img
            src="/images/mark-headshot.jpg"
            alt="Mark Bloomfield"
            width="480"
            height="600"
            loading="lazy"
            class="rounded-3xl w-full object-cover shadow-lg"
          />
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-sand font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Founder · Your Personal AI Guy</p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-green-deep mb-5">Mark Bloomfield</h2>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-muted leading-relaxed">
            <p>
              I spent years as a composites research engineer and sustainability consultant before the AI wave hit. I learned how to think about complex systems, how to separate what's real from what sounds good, and how to explain both to non-technical people.
            </p>
            <p>
              When AI got dramatically better — and when AI search through Claude, ChatGPT, Perplexity, and Google's AI Overviews started rewriting how customers actually find local businesses — I saw a massive gap. The tools and the use cases were real, but nobody was translating any of it for small business owners, so I started doing that work myself.
            </p>
            <p>
              The flagship is the <strong>AI-Ready Website</strong>: a rebuild of your existing site so it actually shows up when customers ask AI tools for a recommendation. Around that, I run strategy sessions for owners who want to figure out where AI fits in their business, and I build custom AI tools when off-the-shelf doesn't quite work.
            </p>
            <p>
              Every engagement is with me directly — I scope it, build it, and support it. I'm based in Boulder, Colorado, working with businesses across the country.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-6 pt-6 border-t border-green-sage/20">
            <p class="text-green-deep font-medium italic">
              "I won't build something for you that I wouldn't build for myself. If it doesn't make sense for your business, I'll tell you that — that's the whole job."
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- OLIVE -->
  <section class="bg-white-warm py-20">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-14 items-center">
        <div class="order-2 md:order-1">
          <p class="text-sand font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Chief Canine Officer</p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-green-deep mb-5">Olive</h2>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-muted leading-relaxed">
            <p>
              Every business needs a CCO. Olive brings unwavering enthusiasm, exceptional listening skills, and zero tolerance for mediocrity — especially when it comes to treats.
            </p>
            <p>
              She supervises all quality control, attends every strategy session (usually from the floor), and reminds me that the best businesses are built on loyalty, showing up every day, and being genuinely happy to hear from customers.
            </p>
            <p>
              Olive's also a reminder of what this work is really about: giving small business owners back the time and peace of mind to spend on what matters most.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="order-1 md:order-2">
          <img
            src="/images/olive.jpg"
            alt="Olive, Chief Canine Officer"
            width="480"
            height="600"
            loading="lazy"
            class="rounded-3xl w-full object-cover shadow-lg"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- VALUES -->
  <section class="bg-cream py-20">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-green-deep mb-12 text-center">What I Stand For</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        {[
          {
            icon: `<svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="8" stroke="#C99356" stroke-width="1.8"/><path d="M18 18l4 4" stroke="#C99356" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>`,
            title: 'Transparency',
            body: "I show you the numbers. You'll know exactly what you're getting, what it costs, and what results to expect. No jargon, no smoke and mirrors.",
          },
          {
            icon: `<svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none"><path d="M14 4v4M14 20v4M4 14h4M20 14h4M7 7l2.8 2.8M18.2 18.2l2.8 2.8M7 21l2.8-2.8M18.2 9.8l2.8-2.8" stroke="#C99356" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>`,
            title: 'Simplicity',
            body: "AI doesn't have to be complicated. I handle every technical detail so you never have to think about infrastructure, APIs, or integrations.",
          },
          {
            icon: `<svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none"><path d="M6 20V14M11 20V10M16 20V6M21 20V12" stroke="#C99356" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>`,
            title: 'Results',
            body: "I measure success in AI-search visibility, leads captured, and time saved. If it's not working, I fix it — that's the whole point.",
          },
        ].map(v => (
          <div class="bg-white-warm rounded-2xl p-8 text-center">
            <div class="flex justify-center mb-4" set:html={v.icon} />
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-green-deep mb-3">{v.title}</h3>
            <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">{v.body}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="bg-green-deep py-20 text-center">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white-warm mb-5">Ready to Work Together?</h2>
      <p class="text-cream/70 mb-8">Start with the free AI Readiness Audit — three minutes, six questions, your top three highest-impact AI opportunities ranked.</p>
      <a href="/ai-audit" class="inline-flex items-center bg-sand text-green-deep font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-xl hover:bg-sand/90 transition-colors">
        Run my free audit
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
